# General ignores
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.md
**/Taskfile.yaml
**/tmp/
**/bin/                # Ignore binaries (they'll be rebuilt)
**/air                 # Dev tool

# Development artifacts
**/vendor/
**/go.sum              # We'll use go.mod for dependency resolution
**/*_test.go
**/testdata/

# Editor/IDE files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Service-specific ignores
services/**/bin/       # All service binaries
services/**/tmp/       # Temporary files

# Documentation assets
docs/assets/           # Large files not needed for runtime

# KEEP these critical paths:
!services/**/configs/  # Need config files
!shared/proto/         # Need protobuf definitions
!shared/gen/go/        # Need generated code